    npcSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2882ea8cc62ca6b4f95e171b4e6c2e78, type: 3}
    lines:
    - 'So my conditions are "num < 20" and "num < 40" and I write the following statements:'
    - "~if(num < 20)\r`\n~{\r`\n~  Bot.say(\"less than 20\");\r`\n~}`"
    - "~else if(num < 40)\r`\n~{\r`\n~  Bot.say(\"more than 20, less than 40\");\r`\n~}`"
    - "~else\r`\n~{\r`\n~  Bot.say(\"more than 40\");\r`\n~}`"
    - 'If num is 10, num < 20 is true and G4wain says "less than 20". If num is 30,
      num > 20 is false so it checks the second condition: num < 40 is true, so G4wain
      says "more than 20, less than 40". And if num is 50 neither condition is true
      so, G4wain says "more than 40".'
  - npcName: Morgan
